<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EduNav OS | The Autonomous Cognitive Campus</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@600;700&family=Urbanist:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-base: #020617;
            --bg-surface: #0f172a;
            --accent: #00E5FF;
            --accent-dim: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #F8FAFC;
            --text-muted: #94A3B8;
            --border: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.15);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-base);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Urbanist', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        /* HEADER NAV */
        header {
            padding: 24px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.8);
        }

        .nav-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .badge-investor {
            background: var(--accent-dim);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* HERO SECTION */
        .hero {
            padding: 100px 0 80px 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -10%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: #000000;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* METRICS SECTION */
        .metrics {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: var(--bg-surface);
            border-y: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .grid-3 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 32px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid-3, .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 40px; }
        }

        .metric-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .metric-num {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .metric-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        /* PRODUCT SECTIONS */
        .section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -10px;
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--accent);
        }

        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .features-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .features-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .features-list i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 4px;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .features-list strong {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* CARD ARCHITECTURE */
        .architecture-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .arch-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px;
        }

        .arch-card i {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .arch-card h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .arch-card p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* STRATEGY COMPARISON TABLE */
        .table-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            overflow-x: auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
        }

        td {
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        tr:hover td {
            background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.02);
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container nav-wrapper">
            <div class="logo">EDUNAV<span>OS</span></div>
            <div class="badge-investor">Seed Stage Data Room</div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <h1>India's First <span>Autonomous Cognitive Campus</span> Platform</h1>
            <p>We leverage a Zero-Cost ERP "Trojan Horse" model to deploy passive BLE Mesh infrastructure across K-12 networks. Moving beyond legacy software, we monetize via scalable B2C safety subscriptions while constructing the world's first verified behavioral data asset: The Grit Index.</p>
            <a href="#architecture" class="btn-primary">Explore Infrastructure Modules</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="metrics">
        <div class="container grid-3">
            <div class="metric-card">
                <div class="metric-num">₹199</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Monthly Parent Subscription</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
                <div class="metric-num">$500K</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Target Seed Capital Round</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
                <div class="metric-num">14 Mo.</div>
                <div class="metric-label">Operational Breakeven Plan</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container grid-2">
            <div>
                <h2 class="section-title">The Disruptive Model</h2>
                <ul class="features-list">
                    <li>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i>
                        <strong>Frictionless Enterprise Acquisition</strong>
                        Our core administrative ERP core is given to institutional chains completely free, removing budget hurdles and blocking out legacy systems.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-tower-broadcast"></i>
                        <strong>Passive IoT Tracking Layer</strong>
                        No manual QR code lines or battery-heavy GPS. Wearable low-power BLE Smart IDs map location points across indoor campus zones instantly.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i>
                        <strong>The Grit Index Pipeline</strong>
                        Passively derived physical consistency logs (punctuality and spatial records) are algorithmically turned into an unmatched behavioral rating system.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="table-wrapper">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Metric</th>
                            <th>Legacy Core (Entab)</th>
                            <th>EduNav Platform</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Software Licensing</strong></td>
                            <td>Upfront Institutional Fees</td>
                            <td><strong>₹0 Free Forever Core</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Tech Deployment</strong></td>
                            <td>Manual Registry Storage</td>
                            <td><strong>Passive BLE Campus Mesh</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Revenue Source</strong></td>
                            <td>School Operating Budgets</td>
                            <td><strong>B2C Parent Subscriptions</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Data Strategy</strong></td>
                            <td>Static Grade Repositories</td>
                            <td><strong>The Behavioral Grit Asset</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="architecture">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 60px;">System Module Distribution</h2>
            <div class="architecture-grid">
                <div class="arch-card">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-button"></i>
                    <h3>01 / Cross-Platform App</h3>
                    <p>Built with Flutter. Delivers instantaneous real-time safety heartbeats, automated communication lines, and transaction gateways for guardians.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="arch-card">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-server"></i>
                    <h3>02 / Serverless Backend</h3>
                    <p>Node.js execution environment utilizing PostgreSQL architectures and Firebase triggers optimized for rapid telemetry packets.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="arch-card">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-microchip"></i>
                    <h3>03 / Embedded Mesh Array</h3>
                    <p>Passive wearable student beacons transmitting secure identifiers to strategically placed stationary and mobile gateway network arrays.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2026 EduNav Technologies. Engineered for Institutional Verification Ecosystems.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent);">edunav.co.in</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
